                                       @RequestParam(name="automatedProject",required=false)
                                       Long projectId)
        Get a generic pipeline page.
        Parameters:
        model - the the model for the current request
        principal - the user in the current request
        locale - the locale that the user is using
        pipelineId - the pipeline to load
        projectId - Project ID to add a AnalysisSubmissionTemplate if necessary (not required)
        Returns:
